{
  "stem": "19969.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "What I found out from the inspector general's report was that he had recommended that several people be tried for the murder of prisoners, some of my men, and then much to my surprise, also some men from the 42nd Division, which puzzled me.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But after I got to reading all the testimony and all the pertinents documents, then long unanswered questions came to light.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Actually, the 42nd Division was involved more than I thought originally.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "What happened was that we had been in there about an hour or so.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And according to the testimony of General Linden, the principal witness, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he said that he came driving up to the camp.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Dachau.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he heard some, he heard some firing inside of the, of the compound.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He then ordered his-- couple of his officers to go in and see what was happening.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, of course, that was my men.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was sporadic firing going on the whole time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In addition to killing the-- some German guards, the men also dispatched a number of large rather vicious guard dogs that were in there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I've never heard that mentioned before by the 42nd or anybody else, but--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They used them to patrol the exterior of, of the prison compound.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were a miscellaneous assortment of dogs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Most of them I saw were Dobermans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But my men shot them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway, I discovered that-- what-- as that came as a surprise to me that prior to my run-in with General Linden and a, a small party, the 42nd had been in there before that.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What happened-- another surprise to me came that nobody ever mentioned the presence of this Marguerite Higgins.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Nobody ever mentioned her presence.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
